have converged on Cleveland.

268
00:17:00,887 --> 00:17:03,321
Every time he plans to kill,
the murder weapon, the m. o.,

269
00:17:03,446 --> 00:17:05,393
and the victimology will all change.

270
00:17:34,698 --> 00:17:37,763
