to give a preliminary profile.

271
00:17:37,932 --> 00:17:39,378
Sure. I gotta go.

272
00:17:40,685 --> 00:17:43,102
I'm gonna step out for this one,
clear my head.

273
00:17:46,455 --> 00:17:47,812
Garcia found 3 male students

274
00:17:47,937 --> 00:17:50,349
enrolled in criminology
classes with felony records.

275
00:17:50,474 --> 00:17:52,745
- Good. We'll interview them.
