352
00:22:13,928 --> 00:22:16,414
He trolled bike paths near
buffalo garroting his victims.

353
00:22:16,539 --> 00:22:18,933
It looks like he copied
everything except for the rape.

354
00:22:19,058 --> 00:22:21,787
Strangulation's a repetition
