359
00:23:04,300 --> 00:23:06,174
H-a-w-k-e-s.

360
00:23:06,936 --> 00:23:08,011
Very good.

361
00:23:10,066 --> 00:23:11,379
I'm Danny.

362
00:23:11,642 --> 00:23:14,808
I want you to call us
if you have any questions at all.

363
00:23:15,945 --> 00:23:17,811
We're gonna take great care of her.

