Something he lost control of.

410
00:25:45,597 --> 00:25:49,114
Or it could be something
he gained control of.

411
00:25:49,239 --> 00:25:50,388
Like himself.

412
00:25:50,833 --> 00:25:54,085
If he's finally defined
himself as a strangler,

413
00:25:54,406 --> 00:25:57,221
